{"tid":1391928,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[越揭越臭] 民生書院校長陳嫣虹 Kuby Chan 涉嫌打壓言論自由","createTime":"2019-07-31T14:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T16:10:04.000Z","uid":292001,"like":228,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"086f6e744bffc74f394a63a0619d44f3b25d04b6","tid":1391928,"uid":292001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:51:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的，前排有個post 爆咗民生書院校長陳嫣虹 Kuby Chan 疑似出咗篇奇文反對反送中運動，已經激到一眾校友紮紮跳。<br />\n<br />\n傳送門：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">(代Friend開po) (奇聞共賞)(傷眼慎入) 民生書院校長Kuby Chan 出Mass Mail鬧反修例運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1362317\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1362317</a><br />\n</span><br />\n之後證實陳嫣虹原來係喺老師whatsapp 群組轉發一位來自馬來西亞牧師 Alvin Cheah 嘅文章，喺呢啲時候轉發呢啲文章，背後目的就真係得陳嫣虹知。<br />\n<br />\n之但係，陳嫣虹你挑起眾多校友諗返起以前被你壓逼嘅歲月，事情又點會咁易解決。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 經過校友們不斷追查，發現陳嫣虹作為一個教育工作者，不但無保持立場中立，甚至打壓老師嘅言論自由，真係枉為一個校長！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罪名一：<br />\n陳嫣虹涉嫌運用校長權力公開一名老師在不記名問卷的回答</span></span><br />\n<br />\n事緣有一次教師發展日，某外籍老師填寫一份不記名問卷時回答了<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">as I don&rsquo;t know any Cantonese, the programme is like a waste of my time!</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n對一個不諳廣東話嘅外籍老師嚟講，參加一個以廣東話為主嘅活動，有負面情緒都好正常。由於問卷係以不記名方式進行，外籍老師就好安心咁如實反映。<br />\n<br />\n點知就出事！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">陳嫣虹之後連續出咗三封mass email 俾老師，雖然無指名道姓，但係人人都知道係針對該名外籍老師。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n嗰幾封email 一出，可以話徹底破壞老師同學校之間嘅信任，甚至令到老師擔心關於學校表現嘅問卷中能否繼續表達一啲改進嘅意見！<br />\n<br />\n有睇唔過眼嘅老師已經就呢件事向校董投訴，下面就係投訴信cap 圖同一啲爆料whatsapp。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fJ5Z3S9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfJ5Z3S9.png&h=9fec47be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CdHxErv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCdHxErv.png&h=65c6133c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罪名二：<br />\n陳嫣虹涉嫌侮辱同學及老師</span></span><br />\n<br />\n陳嫣虹視自己為學校入面最高領導人，為人好戰，唯我獨尊令到同學以及老師們都好憎佢。佢曾經對住全校師生面前公開話反送中運動嘅示威者係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">暴徒</span></span>，暗示遍地開花唔係創意，係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幼稚</span></span>嘅表現。<br />\n<br />\n佢亦會出言侮辱表現不佳嘅老師，批評老師為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">垃圾</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罪名三：<br />\n陳嫣虹涉嫌打壓老師嘅言論自由</span></span><br />\n<br />\n陳嫣虹為咗和諧校內對政治事件嘅立場，公然禁止老師與學生討論政治。曾經有老師因為喺檯頭貼上<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">&rdquo;我要真普選&rdquo;</span></span>而收到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警告信</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外，曾經有老師因為睇唔過眼好言相勸，陳嫣虹事後將該名老師<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">降職</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n罪名二同三請參考以下爆料whatsapp：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C37d8qf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC37d8qf.png&h=a58c695a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此等心胸狹隘，卻又好高騖遠嘅人，真係枉為教育工作者！<br />\n<br />\nOne Last Thing，陳嫣虹總總行徑都顯示佢係一個熱愛中國嘅人，擁有一顆赤色的心，但係佢有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加拿大戶籍</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">有無辦法可以幫呢種人才世世代代留喺大灣區？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以佢對於世界局勢都有中國人嘅見解：<br />\n佢曾經同全校講，中國崛起令到美國唔甘心，所以製造咗一連串政治事件，務求令香港分化，甚至中國滅亡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LFoMJ0y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLFoMJ0y.png&h=0dabeefd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇吓佢同林鄭幾老友！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bOCUSTP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbOCUSTP.png&h=b9c2794d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後講多一句：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">陳嫣虹，恥與為伍！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">最最最後，眾校友請參與8月5日三罷，多你一個真係好多！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">#我係香港人<br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷<br />\n#罷工罷市罷課</span></span>"},{"pid":"993d6131886c91997262ef51ca49f0fcf53debf3","tid":1391928,"uid":257422,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:53:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不要說&quot;推&quot;, <br />\n<br />\n試著用hashtag：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">感謝靚聲絲打讀出 hashtag 無限loop</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/user-612048585/loop\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fuser-612048585%2Floop&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFtArZVC5vK90EjT5EVN%2FGu4%3D&h=3a335f9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/user-612048585/loop</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Hf7ppz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Hf7ppz.png&h=37691996&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/1080/https://na.cx/i/rppcCsL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrppcCsL.png&h=cf9768dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xkS5Vwe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxkS5Vwe.png&h=b234ed26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/1080/https://na.cx/i/TZSULu5.jp